Also the Game [PIC]|publisher=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]|date=|accessdate=2009-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090715084148/http://www.buzzfeed.com/reddit/also-the-work-of-4chan-pic|archive-date=2009-07-15|language=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

