d' « SciTechBlog |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |date=2010-02-12 |accessdate=2010-02-12 |language=en |archive-date=2010-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100215234414/http://scitech.blogs.cnn.com/2010/02/12/4chan-founder-anonymous-speech-is-endangered/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>巴西的《{{link-en|聖保羅州報|O Estado de S. Paulo}}》報導称：「克里斯托弗·普尔参与TED2010會議的事件表明非同尋常的情况的發生……4chan的规则跟所有的網絡公約相反：它处于[[谷歌|谷歌]]、社交網站和博客的對立面。」<ref>{{cite news | author = Leal, Fred | title = Feio, sujo e surreal | work = O Estado de S. Paulo | date = 2010-04-19 | page = L1 | url = http://blogs.estadao.com.br/link/feio-sujo-e-surreal/ | accessdate = 2010-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100909205447/http://blogs.estadao.com.br/link/feio-sujo-e-surreal/ | archivedate = 2010-09-09 | language = pt | dead-url = no }}</ref>

