=== 網絡攻擊 ===
據《華盛頓郵報》称，「在互聯網歷史中，4chan的用户幹了最引人注目的集體行動」。<ref name=Cha>{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/08/09/AR2010080906102.html?hpid=topnews|title=4chan users seize Internet's power for mass disruptions|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|last=Cha|first=Ariana Eunjung|date=2010-08-10|accessdate=2010-08-10|language=en|archive-date=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111042946/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/08/09/AR2010080906102.html?hpid=topnews|dead-url=no}}</ref>

4chan用户“襲擊”了{{link-en|哈尔·特纳|Hal Turner}}——一個秉持[[白人優越主義|白人民族主義]]并否認[[納粹大屠殺|納粹大屠殺]]的博客作者，他的網站遭遇[[分散式阻斷服務攻擊|DDoS攻擊]]，主持的廣播節目也經常受到惡作劇電話干扰。为此特纳起訴4chan和一些其他網站，但是沒成功。<ref name="halsuecopyright">{{cite web| url=http://dockets.justia.com/docket/court-njdce/case_no-2:2007cv00306/case_id-198438/| publisher=Justia 聯邦地區法庭文件| title=Harold C. "Hal" Turner v. 4chan.org| accessdate=2008-07-14| date=2007-01-19| language=en| archive-date=2008-04-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080420131458/http://dockets.justia.com/docket/court-njdce/case_no-2:2007cv00306/case_id-198438/| dead-url=no}}</ref>

