2008年，[[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]的私人[[Yahoo|Yahoo]]電子郵箱帳號密码被一個4chan /b/版用戶破解，<ref name="PalinAP">{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-on-hacker20-2008sep20-story.html|title=Hackers claim break-in to Palin's e-mail account|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|author=Ted Bridis|date=2008-09-17|accessdate=2008-09-17|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308235649/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-on-hacker20-2008sep20-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并被贴在/b/上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theridiculant.metro.co.uk/2008/09/sarah-palins-em.html|title=Sarah Palin's email gets hacked|publisher={{link-en|Metro (英國報紙)|Metro (British newspaper)}}|author=Tom Phillips|date=2008-09-17|accessdate=2008-09-17|language=en|archive-date=2008-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080920105947/http://theridiculant.metro.co.uk/2008/09/sarah-palins-em.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後，另一個/b/用戶把密碼改變了，然後發了截圖，證明他使用佩林的email帳號发送邮件給佩林的朋友，告訴他佩林的帳號被破解，而這個用戶没有把密碼從截圖去掉，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/politics/article/0,8599,1842097,00.html|title=Sarah Palin's E-mail Hacked|publisher=[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]|author=M. J. Stephey|date=2008-09-17|accessdate=2008-09-17|language=en|archive-date=2008-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919092620/http://www.time.com/time/politics/article/0,8599,1842097,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>结果之後许多/b/用戶使用新密碼嘗試登錄，然而帳號却已自動被Yahoo系統封锁了。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/webscout/2008/09/4chans-half-hac.html|title=4Chan's half-hack of Palin's email goes awry|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|author=David Sarno|date=2008-09-17|accessdate=2008-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207083522/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/webscout/2008/09/4chans-half-hac.html|archivedate=2009-02-07|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>事件发生後，美國[[联邦调查局|FBI]]和[[美國特勤局|特勤局]]对此展开調查。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsfactor.com/news/Suspect-Nabbed-in-Palin-E-mail-Hack/story.xhtml?story_id=110003SJWA8K|title=Suspect Nabbed in Palin E-mail Hack|publisher=NewsFactor|author=Steve Bosak|date=2008-09-20|accessdate=2008-09-21|language=en|archive-date=2009-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504145946/http://www.newsfactor.com/news/Suspect-Nabbed-in-Palin-E-mail-Hack/story.xhtml?story_id=110003SJWA8K|dead-url=no}}</ref>此即美国诉大卫·科勒尔案。

