2014年8月，一些互聯網用戶揭露了遊戲媒體中的腐敗醜聞事件<!--"任人唯親"? "裙帶關係"?-->，要點關於女性遊戲開發商{{link-en|佐伊·奎因|Zoe Quinn}}和遊戲記者通姦的指控。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-09-03|url=http://stream.aljazeera.com/story/201409032102-0024126|title=GamerGate: Misogyny or corruption in the gaming community?|publisher=[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]|language=en|accessdate=2014-09-07|archive-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907212404/http://stream.aljazeera.com/story/201409032102-0024126|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-21|url=http://www.returnofkings.com/42109/how-zoe-quinn-screwed-her-way-through-the-video-game-industry?ModPagespeed=noscript|title=How Zoe Quinn Screwed Her Way Through The Video Game Industry|website=Return of Kings|language=en|accessdate=2014-09-07|archive-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907191256/http://www.returnofkings.com/42109/how-zoe-quinn-screwed-her-way-through-the-video-game-industry?ModPagespeed=noscript|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據指控，佐伊和某些電子遊戲新聞網站的記者進行性交，目的為得到好評價的文章，因此引起利益衝突問題。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-19|url=http://talkingship.com/wp/2014/08/19/zoe-quinn-sexual-affairs-ethics/|title=No, Zoe Quinn's Sexual Affairs Aren't a "Private Matter"|website=Talking Ship|language=en|access-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906161137/http://talkingship.com/wp/2014/08/19/zoe-quinn-sexual-affairs-ethics/|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>經過進一步調查，互聯網用戶發現她跟各種遊戲開發商也為了特別的優惠進行性交，其中包括她的雇主（一位已婚男士）。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-19|url=http://www.8cn.tv/content/zoe-quinn-controversy-just-facts|title=The Zoe Quinn Controversy: Just the Facts|website=8CN|language=en|access-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907212432/http://www.8cn.tv/content/zoe-quinn-controversy-just-facts|archive-date=2014-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>關於這事件佐伊表示她認為4chan的/v/版在針對她因為她是女權主義者，受到過大量來自4chan用戶的騷擾和仇恨言論在網絡上，也表示這事件是一種厭惡女人的網絡攻擊。某些網絡媒體用「[[GamerGate|GamerGate]]」（遊戲玩家門）描述此次遊戲產業醜聞事件。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-09-07|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/137293-Exclusive-Zoe-Quinn-Posts-Chat-Logs-Debunking-GamerGate-4Chan-and-Quinn-Respond|title=Exclusive: 4Chan and Quinn Respond to Gamergate Chat Logs|website=The Escapist|language=en|access-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910220217/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/137293-Exclusive-Zoe-Quinn-Posts-Chat-Logs-Debunking-GamerGate-4Chan-and-Quinn-Respond|archive-date=2014-09-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2014-09-03|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/sep/03/gamergate-corruption-games-anita-sarkeesian-zoe-quinn|title=Gamergate: the community is eating itself but there should be room for all|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]|language=en|accessdate=2014-09-07|archive-date=2014-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140916110516/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/sep/03/gamergate-corruption-games-anita-sarkeesian-zoe-quinn|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同月，電子遊戲[[独立游戏|獨立開發者]]{{link-en|菲爾·費舍|Phil Fish}}聲稱他受到4chan /v/用戶的黑客攻擊，並且他本人大量的私人和公司敏感信息被透露。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-22|url=http://www.dailydot.com/geek/4chan-hacks-phil-fish-over-his-defense-of-zoe-quinn/|title=4chan hacks and doxes Zoe Quinn's biggest supporter|website=The Daily Dot|language=en|accessdate=2014-09-07|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006101042/http://www.dailydot.com/geek/4chan-hacks-phil-fish-over-his-defense-of-zoe-quinn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過，客觀證據和他所講的故事有矛盾，黑客的真實身份也不能確認來自/v/——有些懷疑論者認為所謂的黑客攻擊其實是費舍自取的[[假旗行動|假旗行動]]用來責怪/v/，由於事件中各種可疑的漏洞。<ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-25|url=http://mattforney.com/2014/08/25/zoe-quinn-phil-fish-and-the-great-social-justice-swindle/|title=Zoe Quinn, Phil Fish and the Great Social Justice Swindle|website=Matt Forney|language=en}}{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2014-08-22|url=http://www.continue-play.com/news/phil-fish-and-polytron-allegedly-doxxed/|title=Phil Fish and Polytron allegedly doxxed|website=Continue Play|language=en|access-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907190902/http://www.continue-play.com/news/phil-fish-and-polytron-allegedly-doxxed/|archive-date=2014-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 暴力威脅 ===
2006年10月18日，[[美國國土安全部|美國國土安全部]]向[[國家美式橄欖球聯盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]官员警告称恐怖分子可能在体育场使用[[髒彈|髒彈]]。<ref name="bloombergnewsbombthreat">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601079&sid=aVpJWbr6YesA&refer=home|title=Wisconsin Man Is Charged in Fake NFL Stadium Threats|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|accessdate=2006-10-20|author=Chris Dolmetsch, David Voreacos|date=2006-10-20|language=en|archive-date=2012-02-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65kU1cl2f?url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive|dead-url=no}}</ref>情报源为/b/版上一条威胁信息，该信息称在10月22日（[[賴買丹月|賴買丹月]]最后一天）一些体育场将遭袭。<ref name="Internetnewsbombthreat">{{cite web|url=http://www.internetnews.com/bus-news/article.php/3639301|title=Man Charged in Internet Bomb Threats|author=Roy Mark|publisher=InternetNews.com|date=2006-10-20|accessdate=2008-07-24|language=en|archive-date=2008-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080929204214/http://www.internetnews.com/bus-news/article.php/3639301|dead-url=no}}</ref>最后球赛仍未取消，但体育场方面为此仍派遣了大量保安以保证安全。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.abcnews.com/theblotter/2006/10/nfl_stadium_thr.html|title=NFL Stadium Threat: Officials Skeptical But Issue Warning|publisher=[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]|author=Pierre Thomas|date=2006-10-16|accessdate=2008-07-21|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013135928/http://blogs.abcnews.com/theblotter/2006/10/nfl_stadium_thr.html|archive-date=2008-10-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而后在10月20日，一个男子杰克·布拉姆向当局自首，然后由于谎称恐怖袭击的行为而被指控。<ref name="nyctimesnflbombhoax">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/21/us/21stadium.html?ex=1185681600&en=6f5000744e8dd0aa&ei=5070|title=Man, 20, Arrested in Stadium Threat Hoax|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|author=Ronald Smothers|date=2006-10-20|accessdate=2007-07-27|language=en|archive-date=2011-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512060734/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/21/us/21stadium.html?ex=1185681600&en=6f5000744e8dd0aa&ei=5070|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年2月28日，布拉姆在审判中认罪。6月5日，他被判处6个月监禁，6月软禁，并需支付26750美元罚款。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/224745/man_gets_six_months_posting_terror_threat_online/|title=Man gets six months for posting terror threat online|work=Computerworld|author=Sharon Gaudin|date=2008-06-16|accessdate=2008-07-21|language=en|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012091906/http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/224745/man_gets_six_months_posting_terror_threat_online/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2007年9月11日午夜，一個學生贴出一些照片，其中有他本人扛着（假）炸彈的场景。<ref name="threat">{{cite web|url=http://4chanarchive.org/brchive/dspl_thread.php5?thread_id=39101047|title=4chanarchive — Thread 39101047|publisher=4chanarchive.com|accessdate=2008-01-18|date=2007-09-11|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080105081944/http://4chanarchive.org/brchive/dspl_thread.php5?thread_id=39101047|archive-date=2008-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他在信息裡威脅要炸自己所在的美國[[德克萨斯州|德州]]普弗拉熱維爾中學：

{{Cquote|{{lang|en|Hello, /b/.
On September 11, 2007, at 9:11 A.M. Central time, two pipe bombs will be remote-detonated at Pflugerville High School.
Promptly after the blast, I, along with two ther[sic] Anonymous, will charge the building, armed with a Bushmaster AR-15, IMI Galil AR, a vintage, government-issue M1 .30 Carbine, and a Benelli M4 semi auto shotgun.}}

你好，/b/。

